Titolo: Dreams (video game)

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Dreams is a game creation system and service developed by Media Molecule and published by Sony Interactive Entertainment for the PlayStation 4, which released on 14 February 2020. It includes several games developed in Dreams by Media Molecule, including Art's Dream, Ancient Dangers: A Batâ€™s Tale, and several VR mini-games, with access to other games and user-generated content. Players can create user-generated content in the form of fully-fledged games, animated movies, music, sculptures, art, game mechanics, and game assets, which can be shared or remixed to be used in others' creations. Other players can indulge in such unique user-generated content.



Genere: Game creation system

Valutazione: N/A
